lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur should start behaving like a big team and not worry about north London rivals Arsenal overtaking them in the Premier League, manager Mauricio Pochettino has said.

headline.print_headline: Pochettino Keen to Bring Big Club Mentality to Spurs
headline.main: Pochettino Keen to Bring Big Club Mentality to Spurs
